OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBrazil recognises six new  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Findigenous reserves        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Brazilian President Luiz Inacio Lula da
OL,6, Silva has decreed six new indigenous   
OL,7, reserves, banning mining and           
OL,8, restricting commercial farming there.  
OL,10,FThe lands - including a vast area of   
OL,11,FAmazon rainforest - cover about 620,000
OL,12,Fhectares (1.5m acres).                 
OL,14,FIndigenous leaders welcomed the move,  
OL,15,Fbut said more areas needed protection. 
OL,17,FLula, who took office in January, has  
OL,18,Fpledged to reverse policies of his     
OL,19,Ffar-right predecessor Jair Bolsonaro,  
OL,20,Fwho promoted mining in indigenous      
OL,21,Flands.                                 
